All Classes

Class Description
Advanced_graph
This class contains Neo4J advanced queries.
Advanced_mongo
This class contains MongoDB advanced queries made with aggregation pipeline.
Crud_graph
Contains basic CRUD operation that are executed on Social Wine
Crud_mongo
Contains all the basic CRUD operation done on MongoDB
DbOperations
Class that contains all CRUD operations and complex method of Neo4J and MongoDB together.
InitTh
Start thread for scraping and keep it on for a period of time.
Main
In the main class is called the scraper and the menu.
Menu
Contains the two mains menus (Admin/User/Unregistered user).
Populating_function_social
Contains a method that take all the reviews that are stored inside MongoDB and add them inside Neo4J
Populating_wine_document
Contains a method that takes all data from original json file and put them inside wines collection in MongoDB, creating array of nested document.
ResultsNotFoundException
Raised when for one query the result set is empty
Review
Review entity.
ReviewAlreadyInserted
Raised when a review is already inserted
ScraperThread
Contains scraper that allow to retrieve new reviews from winemag website.
ServerWinmagOufOfServiceException
Contains the ServerWinmagOutOfServiceException that is raised if for some reason the Winmag website is down.
User
User entity.
UserNotPresentException
Raised when a user doesn't exists
Wine
Wine entity
WineNotExistsException
Raised when a given wine doesn't exists
WrongInsertionException
Raised when user insert string instead of numbers or viceversa.
